General.Name: Ginar Technology Co Ltd
General.Description: Ginar Technology Co.,Ltd. engages in the research, development, and production of engineering plastic and composite materials in Taiwan and China. It offers GITOP HPPA engineering plastics, such as high performance nylon composite engineering plastic; MAPEX polyamide engineering plastics, including polyamide 6, polyamide 66, and high temperature nylon compounds; APLAX polypropylene engineering plastics comprising polypropylene compounds; and KAPEX polycarbonate engineering plastics. Its products are used in materials for automotive, sports, daily use, consumer electronics, and electrical and electronics. The company was founded in 1982 and is headquartered in Taoyuan City, Taiwan.
